modName: Retexture of Tera cfl18 armour for CBBE
summary: This is a retexture of one of the armours from asianboy345\'s super TERA Armor Collection UNP that was redone for CBBE by Nausicaa.   My intent is to do something similar to the others great armours in the collection and make available if there is any interest.
descriptionHtml:
This is a retexture of one of the armours from asianboy345\'s TERA Armor Collection UNP that was redone for CBBE by Nausicaa.  You need to first install the Tera armors - cfl02 cfl18 hefh16 Hefh19 - CBBE By Nausicaa found here: http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/28258.  My intent is to do something similar to the others great armours in the collection and make available if there is any interest.

If you have a UNP body you can use my mod found here: http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/35931

Upload any photos you take.

Thank you asianboy345 for permission to do this retexture.

Requirements
========================================================================================
Tera armors - cfl02 cfl18 hefh16 Hefh19 - CBBE By Nausicaa
Calientes Female Body Mod Big Bottom Edition v3.2.3
Skyrim v1.8
